#: ../../../release/2.3.4-notes.rst:5
msgid "NumPy 2.3.4 Release Notes"
msgstr "NumPy 2.3.4 發行備註"

#: ../../../release/2.3.4-notes.rst:7
msgid ""
"The NumPy 2.3.4 release is a patch release split between a number of "
"maintenance updates and bug fixes. This release supports Python versions "
"3.11-3.14. This release is based on the Python 3.14.0 final."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release/2.3.4-notes.rst:13
msgid "Changes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release/2.3.4-notes.rst:15
msgid ""
"The ``npymath`` and ``npyrandom`` libraries now have a ``.lib`` rather than "
"a ``.a`` file extension on win-arm64, for compatibility for building with "
"MSVC and ``setuptools``. Please note that using these static libraries is "
"discouraged and for existing projects using it, it's best to use it with a "
"matching compiler toolchain, which is ``clang-cl`` on Windows on Arm."
msgstr ""

